function Index() { const TAGS = ["Show all", "Auction", "Buy Now"] const MENU = ["Useless", "Condition", "Delivery options"] const OPTIONS = ["Related", "worldwide shipping", "under $50", "kitten", "plastic plugs", "pucker shoes", "vintage typewriter"] return (
{MENU.map(menu => ( {menu} ))}
{TAGS.map(tags => ( {tags} ))}
{OPTIONS.map(option => ( {option} ))}
) } export default Index
